OL,3,CIslanders urge Blue Islands to improve
OL,4,Cservices after flight disruptions
OL,6,FAirline customers have threatened they
OL,7,Fwill never use Blue Islands again and
OL,8,Fare calling for the company to improve
OL,9,Fits services following delays and
OL,10,Fcancellations of numerous flights.
OL,12,FIt comes after customers do not get
OL,13,Fcompensation for the cancellations or
OL,14,Fdelays to their flights because of
OL,15,Fregional differences in laws.
OL,17,FThe legislation means that those
OL,18,Fdeparting from or are not entitled to
OL,19,Freimbursement as the Channel Islands
OL,20,Fis not part of the European Union or
OL,21,Fthe United Kingdom.
