OL,3,CIslanders urge Blue Islands to improve
OL,4,Cservices after flight disruptions
OL,6,FHowever, the Minister for Sustainable
OL,7,FEconomic Development, Deputy Kirsten
OL,8,FMorel says it is something he will
OL,9,Flook at.
OL,11,FBlue Islands customer, Conor Walsh had
OL,12,Fto spend hundreds of pounds after his
OL,13,Fflight was cancelled to Dublin, he
OL,14,Fexplains: "They called me and said 'we
OL,15,Fare really sorry but we don't pay any
OL,16,Fexpenses', I replied saying that the
OL,17,Fcompany had told me on two occasions
OL,18,Fyou did."
