OL,3,CIslanders urge Blue Islands to improve
OL,4,Cservices after flight disruptions
OL,6,F"It was shambolic and the fact they
OL,7,Fhaven't responded to any of my
OL,8,Fcorrespondents since then, it is just
OL,9,Fvery very poor, Blue Islands just
OL,10,Fblanked us essentially."
OL,12,F"It is pretty poor that there is no
OL,13,Flegislation in Jersey for this,
OL,14,Fespecially because flights get
OL,15,Fcancelled here quite a lot because of
OL,16,Ffog or whatever so it is something
OL,17,Fthat should be looked at."
