OL,3,CIslanders urge Blue Islands to improve
OL,4,Cservices after flight disruptions
OL,6,FHe adds: "We were in the airport for
OL,7,Fat least seven hours, within a six-
OL,8,Fyear-old so trying to also keep them
OL,9,Fentertained was difficult and it is
OL,10,Fstressful."
OL,12,F"A lot of people we spoke to on the
OL,13,Fplane had similar experiences, or
OL,14,Fperhaps even worse than ours and they
OL,15,Fsaid they would never fly with them
OL,16,Fagain".
