OL,3,CIslanders urge Blue Islands to improve
OL,4,Cservices after flight disruptions
OL,6,FDeputy Kirsten Morel says the lack of
OL,7,Freliability in flights is worrying, he
OL,8,Fsays: "This is concerning because
OL,9,Fconnectivity is at the heart of
OL,10,Feverything I have been trying to do.
OL,12,F"Having reliable and frequent
OL,13,Fconnections to the UK and Europe are
OL,14,Fvital for Jersey's functioning
OL,15,Feconomy."
