OL,3,CIslanders urge Blue Islands to improve
OL,4,Cservices after flight disruptions
OL,6,FHe adds: "It does highlight the need
OL,7,Ffor travel insurance, we don't have
OL,8,Fthose same regulations here so
OL,9,Foutbound flights are not protected,
OL,10,Fbut your incoming flights are
OL,11,Fprotected, so it is a slightly strange
OL,12,Fsituation."
OL,14,FWhen asked if this law is something he
OL,15,Fwould look to introduce, he says: "It
OL,16,Fis something I am happy to look at but
OL,17,Fit would mean higher prices as a
OL,18,Fresult and so you need to bear that in
OL,19,Fmind.
