OL,3,CIslanders urge Blue Islands to improve
OL,4,Cservices after flight disruptions
OL,6,F"It is something I would consider but
OL,7,Fdon't plan on changing at the moment."
OL,9,FChief Executive of Guernsey Cricket,
OL,10,FCarl Brooks says he would like to
OL,11,Fdiscuss changes the company should
OL,12,Fmake after the team were left stranded
OL,13,Fin Jersey because of a cancelled
OL,14,Fflight.
OL,16,FCarl Brooks says: "We want a
OL,17,Fconstructive relationship with them as
OL,18,Fthey're an important partner for us
OL,19,Fand therefore we have to work with
OL,20,FBlue Islands and we want to do that
OL,21,Fproductively.
