OL,6,F"So what we can do to help them
OL,7,Fimprove their communications, customer
OL,8,Fcare, and safeguarding approach is
OL,9,Fsomething that we'd like to talk to
OL,10,Fthem about."
OL,12,FTheairline has apologised and says it
OL,13,Fis "experiencing supply chain
OL,14,Fchallenges resulting in a shortage of
OL,15,Faircraft components."
