OL,3,CIslanders urge Blue Islands to improve
OL,4,Cservices after flight disruptions
OL,6,FIn a statement, the airline says:
OL,7,F"Blue Islands is experiencing supply
OL,8,Fchain challenges resulting in a
OL,9,Fshortage of aircraft components and
OL,10,Fparts which has impacted our and other
OL,11,Foperators', release of aircraft from
OL,12,Fscheduled maintenance
OL,14,F"Operational resilience was further
OL,15,Fimpacted by two unforeseen technical
OL,16,Fissues at the weekend which disrupted
OL,17,Fflights including Sunday evening's
OL,18,Fflight from Jersey to Guernsey."
