OL,4,Cservices after flight disruptions
OL,6,FBlue Islands adds: "A third-party
OL,7,Foperator has been brought in to
OL,8,Fsupport the schedule; there is
OL,9,Fincreased complexity to this
OL,11,Fprocess in a post-Brexit environment,
OL,12,Fadding to the timescale for utilising
OL,13,Fthis type of provision.
OL,15,F"There will also be some schedule
OL,16,Fadjustments made to provide some
OL,17,Foperational resilience, any affected
OL,18,Fpassengers will be advised as soon as
OL,19,Fpossible."
